WEBVTT

00:00:59.685 --> 00:01:02.471
She went over to her, and she said,
"What are you drawing?"

00:01:02.495 --> 00:01:04.894
And the girl said,
"I'm drawing a picture of God."

00:01:04.918 --> 00:01:08.330
And the teacher said,
"But nobody knows what God looks like."

00:01:08.354 --> 00:01:10.426
And the girl said,
"They will in a minute."

00:01:10.450 --> 00:01:12.950
(Laughter)

00:01:16.710 --> 00:01:18.730
CA: The idea he spoke about

00:01:18.754 --> 00:01:21.230
seemed to really
strike a nerve with people.

00:01:21.254 --> 00:01:24.283
It felt as if millions and millions
of people around the world

00:01:24.307 --> 00:01:26.848
had had this experience of being at school

00:01:26.872 --> 00:01:32.109
and somehow, their own creativity
not being heard or recognized